698
00:43:56,040 --> 00:43:59,240
I just wanted to warn you and...

699
00:44:03,400 --> 00:44:05,600
apologize for the past.

700
00:44:07,760 --> 00:44:09,720
It was my fault

701
00:44:09,760 --> 00:44:11,650
