I was just pressuring you

703
00:44:16,440 --> 00:44:18,600
and forcing a yes.

704
00:44:20,000 --> 00:44:21,800
I'm sorry.

705
00:44:25,400 --> 00:44:27,000
I'm sorry, too.

706
00:44:27,640 --> 00:44:30,040
I didn't know what to do,

707
00:44:30,760 --> 00:44:32,800
